    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115491_3_2793-2885",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2793-2885",
      "markText": "脖子细细的，看样子是刚从乡下雇上来的黄毛丫头，还没开过胯，还没经过大阵仗。正是这样的生坯子，用起来才有些意思。女人身上一旦起了软肉，就不再是柴鸡的味道，而是用化学饲料催长的肉鸡的味道。",
      "totalCount": 704,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115491&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2793&rangeEnd=2885",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fa32e70813ab939dg011ede?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2793&rangeEnd=2885"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115491_3_1514-1600",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1514-1600",
      "markText": "他们的心思也不在酒上，而是在车站广场那些“两条腿的动物”上。俩人漫不经心地呷着白酒。嘴里有味无味地咀嚼着四条腿动物的杂碎，四只眼睛通过三面开口的小饭店，不住地向人群中睃寻。",
      "totalCount": 660,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115491&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1514&rangeEnd=1600",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fa32e70813ab939dg011ede?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1514&rangeEnd=1600"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115491_3_1950-2022",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1950-2022",
      "markText": "唐朝阳和宋金明不能明白，元旦也好，春节也罢，只不过都是时间上的说法，又不是人的发情期，那些数不清的男人和女人，干吗为此变得慌里慌张、躁动不安呢？",
      "totalCount": 588,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115491&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1950&rangeEnd=2022",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fa32e70813ab939dg011ede?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1950&rangeEnd=2022"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115491_17_2249-2309",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "2249-2309",
      "markText": "“我死后，你就说我俩是冒顶砸死的，你一定要跟窑主说我是你的亲二叔，跟窑主要两万块钱，你就回家好好上学，哪儿也不要去了！”",
      "totalCount": 550,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115491&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=2249&rangeEnd=2309",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fa32e70813ab939dg011ede?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=2249&rangeEnd=2309"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115491_4_3709-3788",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3709-3788",
      "markText": "像这种老实蛋子，虽然也有一把子力气，但到哪里都挣不到什么钱，既养活不了老婆，也养活不了孩子。这样的笨蛋只适合给别人当点子，让别人拿他的人命一次性地换一笔钱花。",
      "totalCount": 520,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115491&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3709&rangeEnd=3788",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fa32e70813ab939dg011ede?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3709&rangeEnd=3788"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115491_4_4261-4300",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4261-4300",
      "markText": "老妇人这才抬起头来，但很快又把头磕下去，说：“好人一路平安，好人一路平安……”",
      "totalCount": 493,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115491&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4261&rangeEnd=4300",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fa32e70813ab939dg011ede?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4261&rangeEnd=4300"
    },
    {
